  "title": "Potential and Prospects of Introducing Chickpea into Sri Lanka: A Review of Earlier Research",
  "abstract": "Traditionally, chickpea is not cultivated in Sri Lanka and its entire demand (9700 t annually) is met through imports. Following a brief review of some of the limited studies performed on chickpea in Sri Lanka, the prospects and potential for chickpea cultivation are considered.",
